<p>Hi <%= name %>,</p>

<p>You have <a href="<%= site_root %>/notifications"><%= notifications_count %></a> waiting for you at Exercism.io.<p>
<% if truncated? %>
<p>Here are the most recent ones:</p>
<% end %>
<% if notifications %>
  <p>
    <% notifications.each do |notification| %>
      <li>
        <a href="<%= site_root + notification.link %>">
          <%= notification.language %>: <%= notification.slug %>
        </a>
        <%= notification.regarding %> <%= from(notification.creator) %> <i><%= ago(notification.created_at) %></i>
      </li>
    <% end %>
  </p>
<% end %>

<% if pending_submissions.any? %>
*********
  <p>
    Spare a few minutes? Help out others by reviewing these submissions.
    <% pending_submissions.each do |submission| %>
      <li>
        <a href="<%= site_root %>/submissions/<%= submission.key %>"><%= submission.track_id %>: <%= submission.slug %></a>
        <%= submission.user.username %>
        submitted this exercise <%= ago(submission.created_at) %>
      </li>
    <% end %>
  </p>
<% end %>

</br>
--</br>
If you'd like to stop receiving email notifications, go to <a href="<%= site_root %>/<%= @user.username %>"><%= site_root %>/<%= @user.username %></a> and delete your email address.

Do you have thoughts? Ideas? Criticism? I'd love to hear from you. Hit reply to send me an email.
